{"vv16:0.1":"Vimanavatthu ","vv16:0.2":"Itthivimana ","vv16:0.3":"Pithavagga ","vv16:0.4":"16. Sirimavimanavatthu ","vv16:1.1":"“Yutta ca te paramaalankata haya, ","vv16:1.2":"Adhomukha aghasigama bali java; ","vv16:1.3":"Abhinimmita pancarathasata ca te, ","vv16:1.4":"Anventi tam sarathicodita haya. ","vv16:2.1":"Sa titthasi rathavare alankata, ","vv16:2.2":"Obhasayam jalamiva joti pavako; ","vv16:2.3":"Pucchami tam varatanu anomadassane, ","vv16:2.4":"Kasma nu kaya anadhivaram upagami”. ","vv16:3.1":"“Kamaggapattanam yamahunuttaram, ","vv16:3.2":"Nimmaya nimmaya ramanti devata; ","vv16:3.3":"Tasma kaya acchara kamavannini, ","vv16:3.4":"Idhagata anadhivaram namassitum”. ","vv16:4.1":"“Kim tvam pure sucaritamacaridha, ","vv16:4.2":"Kenacchasi tvam amitayasa sukhedhita; ","vv16:4.3":"Iddhi ca te anadhivara vihangama, ","vv16:4.4":"Vanno ca te dasa disa virocati. ","vv16:5.1":"Devehi tvam parivuta sakkata casi, ","vv16:5.2":"Kuto cuta sugatigatasi devate; ","vv16:5.3":"Kassa va tvam vacanakaranusasanim, ","vv16:5.4":"Acikkha me tvam yadi buddhasavika”ti. ","vv16:6.1":"“Nagantare nagaravare sumapite, ","vv16:6.2":"Paricarika rajavarassa sirimato; ","vv16:6.3":"Nacce gite paramasusikkhita ahum, ","vv16:6.4":"Sirimati mam rajagahe avedimsu. ","vv16:7.1":"Buddho ca me isinisabho vinayako, ","vv16:7.2":"Adesayi samudayadukkhaniccatam; ","vv16:7.3":"Asankhatam dukkhanirodhasassatam, ","vv16:7.4":"Maggancimam akutilamanjasam sivam. ","vv16:8.1":"Sutvanaham amatapadam asankhatam, ","vv16:8.2":"Tathagatassanadhivarassa sasanam; ","vv16:8.3":"Silesvaham paramasusamvuta ahum, ","vv16:8.4":"Dhamme thita naravarabuddhadesite. ","vv16:9.1":"Natvanaham virajapadam asankhatam, ","vv16:9.2":"Tathagatenanadhivarena desitam; ","vv16:9.3":"Tatthevaham samathasamadhimaphusim, ","vv16:9.4":"Sayeva me paramaniyamata ahu. ","vv16:10.1":"Laddhanaham amatavaram visesanam, ","vv16:10.2":"Ekamsika abhisamaye visesiya; ","vv16:10.3":"Asamsaya bahujanapujita aham, ","vv16:10.4":"Khiddaratim paccanubhomanappakam. ","vv16:11.1":"Evam aham amatadasamhi devata, ","vv16:11.2":"Tathagatassanadhivarassa savika; ","vv16:11.3":"Dhammaddasa pathamaphale patitthita, ","vv16:11.4":"Sotapanna na ca pana matthi duggati. ","vv16:12.1":"Sa vanditum anadhivaram upagamim, ","vv16:12.2":"Pasadike kusalarate ca bhikkhavo; ","vv16:12.3":"Namassitum samanasamagamam sivam, ","vv16:12.4":"Sagarava sirimato dhammarajino. ","vv16:13.1":"Disva munim muditamanamhi pinita, ","vv16:13.2":"Tathagatam naravaradammasarathim; ","vv16:13.3":"Tanhacchidam kusalaratam vinayakam, ","vv16:13.4":"Vandamaham paramahitanukampakan”ti. ","vv16:14.1":"Sirimavimanam solasamam. "}